005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Chief Executive is responsible for the delivery of the agency’s services and is the ‘accounting officer’ for the budget. He is also an executive member of the Animal Health and Welfare Board for England.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2021-07-02T15:12:18Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Interim Chief Executive","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"8477a549-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Director of Service Delivery is responsible for the delivery of field services and leading the agency’s disease outbreak response.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2021-07-02T15:11:40Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Interim Director of Service Delivery (Jobshare)","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"8477a36d-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Director of Scientific Services is responsible for the leadership and management of science delivery across the agency.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2014-10-01T10:02:15Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director of Scientific Services","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"8477a2cc-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Veterinary Director is responsible for the leadership and management of veterinary services delivery across the agency.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-07-15T11:44:46Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Veterinary Director","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"8477a4b1-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Director of Corporate Services is responsible for Finance and Procurement, Estates, Information Management and Technology. Commercial Services, Relationship Management, and Audit and Risk in APHA.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2014-10-01T10:05:11Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director of Corporate Services","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"84783906-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Director of Plant and Bee Health is responsible for the Plant Health and Seeds Inspectorate, the Bee Inspectorate, the Plant Varieties and Seeds Group and the GM Inspectorate in APHA.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2015-01-23T10:11:53Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director of Plant and Bee Health","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"7613a3c1-6871-4ce5-94ec-d8625b1b3613","details":{"body":"<p>The Finance Director is responsible for the oversight and management of APHA’s budget and ensuring the agency effectively manages its finances.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-04-01T11:18:33Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Finance Director","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"d55e54e1-1a8c-4b1e-a560-a2772cd92798","details":{"body":"<p>The Director for EU Exit and Trade at APHA is responsible for leading APHA activity to deliver a successful EU Exit.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2018-02-06T13:00:18Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director for EU Exit and Trade","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"e26d687d-cdcb-4ec7-b862-2ea4dcd1e62a","details":{"body":"<p>Interim Director of Service Delivery responsible for EU Borders development, SR21 and Corporate Services liaison.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2021-07-02T15:11:19Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Interim Director of Service Delivery (Jobshare)","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"d6fb1f24-2a35-4cb4-9096-6b6e11dc8e43","details":{"body":"<p>The Director of Science leads the delivery of APHA’s scientific research and services and is the senior end user for the National Biosecurity Centre Programme to develop the science facilities and capability at APHA Weybridge.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-06-17T15:09:29Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director of Science","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"0113ce94-16aa-41c7-a95a-2d34826a92b4","details":{"body":"<p>The Interim Chief Executive is responsible for the delivery of the agency’s services and is the ‘accounting officer’ for the budget. The Interim Chief Executive is also an executive member of the Animal Health and Welfare Board for England.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-07-01T10:15:21Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Interim Chief Executive","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"4e749222-302c-42d5-b75f-28d57ddb6301","details":{"body":"\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2022-05-12T15:18:00Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director of Service Delivery","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"97da53b5-f70e-4812-8734-cd78ef190170","details":{"body":"<p>The Director of Service Delivery is responsible for the delivery of field services and leading the agency’s disease outbreak response.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2022-07-20T10:09:26Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Interim Director of Service Delivery (Jobshare)","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"c7152f14-8ca7-4e60-9772-0f10571b87f2","details":{"body":"<p>This director oversees and leads APHA’s delivery of operational services for animal, plant and bee health. This includes the agency’s network of customer service centres.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-04-15T14:36:43Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director of Animal and Plant Delivery Services","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"0db3083d-a70c-4b36-85a6-5ed5aa7eafd1","details":{"body":"<p>The Scientific Services Director will be responsible to the APHA Science and Transformation Director for the quality and integrity of the agency’s science services and scientific colleagues.</p>\n\n<p>The role will be responsible for ensuring that the scientific perspective is at the heart of decision making in the agency, playing a key part in developing the strategic thinking and direction of the agency.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2023-01-17T16:21:34Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Scientific Services Director","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"6a197707-d799-4c6f-8c92-b3a1a3e99433","details":{"body":"<p>The Veterinary Director is responsible for the leadership of veterinary services across the agency.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-07-14T10:02:24Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Veterinary Director","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"8e554ac6-1cb7-45ac-bdf7-68a7e40fdfff","details":{"body":"<p>The Director of Science Operations and Research is responsible for:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>the operational delivery of science related matters in the Animal and Plant Health Agency (APHA)</li>\n  <li>the quality and integrity of APHA’s science services and scientific colleagues</li>\n  <li>making sure that the scientific perspective is part of decision making in APHA</li>\n</ul>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-06-19T13:34:32Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Interim Director of Science Operations and Research","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"ef6ff78a-7f4b-401c-848b-ee88cbbca21a","details":{"body":"<p>This director leads on the science specifications for the new biocontainment animal and laboratory facilities as part of the APHA Weybridge site redevelopment.</p>\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-04-15T15:36:01Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director for National Biosecurity Centre, Weybridge","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"0ca3f630-f1c1-4dae-9f55-c2aba09c1e8d","details":{"body":"<p>The Transformation Director leads and manages transformation across the Animal and Plant Health Agency (APHA).</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-05-20T12:57:00Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Transformation Director ","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"12b565b8-6777-496b-bab1-182d3e9a5dc3","details":{"body":"<p>The chief executive is the chair of APHA’s Executive Board, responsible for the delivery of APHA’s services, and is the accounting officer for the agency’s budget.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-06-23T14:38:22Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chief Executive","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"7a918c32-cd9a-4a8c-9b3a-8bbee3ab40e7","details":{"body":"<p>The APHA Human Resources (HR) Director leads the team of Defra group HR Business Partners (BPs). They support APHA employees with HR policy, resourcing and employee relations.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-07-30T14:52:20Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Human Resources Director","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"32343cc8-ec1a-41e7-ba62-f8db7e35a5c0","details":{"body":"<p>This director is responsible for:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>the operational delivery of science and research in APHA</li>\n  <li>the quality and integrity of APHA’s scientific se